pose of triangulating the love interest and galvanizing the wholesome "family values" of this play by a jolt of supercharged passion.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / European / General.2bisacsh1 aArgent, Geoffrey Alan.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPenn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014z978311074526940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780271061665?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780271061665423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780271061665/original  a978-3-11-074526-9  Penn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK